      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW LILIBET (1) boasts strong form at this course and distance having won two times from three starts. Below best last time at Wagga (19.09) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths fifth. Expected to go close. IRINKA FRED (2) stuck on well last time to finish 1.75 lengths back in third (18.79) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 330m. Can measure up. BALMORAL QUEEN (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (25.15) in a Grade 4/5 at Goulburn. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. A big run wouldn't surprise. LET'S GO OUT (8) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - should be thereabouts.",
